data.description: Combine top New York City attractions on a guided bus tour and the Staten Island Ferry. With insider commentary from your guide, visit Rockefeller Center, South Street Seaport, 9/11 Memorial, and Wall Street. Take a ferry ride to Staten Island, with views of Ellis Island, the Statue of Liberty, and the Brooklyn Bridge. Back on the ground, visit Lincoln Center and Central Park before ending this whirlwind tour.

New York City's Chinatown offers some of the best food in the US, but if you don't know the places to go, you could seriously miss out. This New York Chinatown food tour takes you to popular restaurants and hidden gems to try delicious food and learn about the history of the area. Plus, this tour runs with just eight other people, so you'll get personalized attention from your guide.

Rediscover New York City, this time from the sky, on this exciting helicopter tour. Fly around the Five Boroughs and see some of the city's tourist highlights from above, including Central Park, the Empire State Building, and the Statue of Liberty. Get a different perspective on life in the Big Apple, you might even discover some new places to visit when you play again!

Experience the magic of Hollywood and see where your favorite movies were made during this guided tour of the Warner Bros. Studio. Join your guide and a small group to explore sound stages and background scenes, see the famous Central Perk cafe from Friends, and learn about green screen technology. For a grand finale, take part in your favorite DC Universe and Harry Potter movies in recreated sets.

data.titleActivity: Hollywood Movie Studios and Celebrities Full-Day Private Tour
data.description: Madame Tussauds Hollywood allows you to pose right next to your favorite celebrities. Featuring wax figures of more than 125 celebrities, including Hollywood stars, the interactive museum invites you into a world of fame for a day, without velvet ribbons or barriers. Includes admission to the 4-D Marvel Super Hero Experience.

data.titleActivity: Visit to Madame Tussauds Hollywood Wax Museum
data.description: Explore Hollywood and beyond on this full-day guided tour. After a hotel pickup, meet up with a knowledgeable and entertaining guide and see sights like the Hollywood sign, Dolby and Chinese theaters, and the Walk of Fame. Visit major movie studios and see the homes of movie stars, cruise the Sunset Strip, and visit Melrose Place and Rodeo Drive in Beverly Hills.
